@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Public Users" as users
actor "Analyst/Admin" as admin

rectangle "Input" as input {
  [Reddit Posts]
}

rectangle "Process" as process {
  [Scrape]
  [Validate]
  [Analyze Text (NLP)]
  [Map Locations]
  [Cluster Hotspots]
}

rectangle "NLP" as nlp {
  [Sentiment]
  [Sarcasm]
  [Emotions]
}

rectangle "Data Store" as data {
  database "Supabase" as db
}

rectangle "Output" as output {
  [Heatmap]
  [Analytics]
  [Grievance Feed]
}

users --> input : public posts
input --> process : raw data
process --> nlp : text signals
nlp --> data : save results
process --> data : save clean posts
data --> output : dashboard data
output --> admin : decisions

note right of process
Theoretical framework
follows Input-Process-Output
(IPO) model with NLP and
geospatial analytics as
core processing layers.
end note

@enduml
